&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://thar.be/spider.png" alt="Spider graph using Gruff"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And of course, like everything in Gruff, it&amp;#8217;s fully themable.&lt;/p&gt;

